metadata.Title: CVE-2016-5033 on Ubuntu 21.04 (hirsute) - medium.
metadata.Description: The print_exprloc_content function in libdwarf before 20160923 allows remote attackers to cause a denial of service (out-of-bounds read) via a crafted file.

criterions.comment: dwarfutils package in hirsute, is related to the CVE in some way and has been fixed (note: '20160507+git20160523.9086738-1').
